### Optional add-ons

Extend the power of your Site plan with these optional add-ons.

*   Optimize
    
    Maximize conversions from your site. Starting at $299/mo.
    
    *   ![Image 39](https://dhygzobemt712.cloudfront.net/Icons/Dark/24px/CircleCheckYes.svg)
        
        ### Easily set up and conduct experiments
        
        Compare different variations across your site to determine what performs best.
        
    *   ![Image 40](https://dhygzobemt712.cloudfront.net/Icons/Dark/24px/CircleCheckYes.svg)
        
        ### Target with personalization
        
        Tailor your site experiences to individual visitor behaviors.
        
    *   ![Image 41](https://dhygzobemt712.cloudfront.net/Icons/Dark/24px/CircleCheckYes.svg)
        
        ### Use AI to optimize your visitor experience
        
        Let AI make real-time decisions to surface the right content to the right visitors.
        
    
*   Analyze
    
    Get actionable insights on your site performance. Starting at $29/mo.
    
    *   ![Image 42](https://dhygzobemt712.cloudfront.net/Icons/Dark/24px/CircleCheckYes.svg)
        
        ### The data you need, where you need it
        
        Get a unified view of site performance right within Webflow.
        
    *   ![Image 43](https://dhygzobemt712.cloudfront.net/Icons/Dark/24px/CircleCheckYes.svg)
        
        ### Insights you’ll immediately understand
        
        Get contextual insights presented in an intuitive, digestible way.
        
    *   ![Image 44](https://dhygzobemt712.cloudfront.net/Icons/Dark/24px/CircleCheckYes.svg)
        
        ### Effortless, code-free setup
        
        No manual configuration needed — thanks to one-click setup and automatic event capture.
        
    
*   Localization
    
    Localize your site for audiences around the world. Starting at $9/mo.
    
    *   ![Image 45](https://dhygzobemt712.cloudfront.net/Icons/Dark/24px/CircleCheckYes.svg)
        
        ### Visually customize your locale
        
        From design to content, fully customize your site for your target locales — no code required.
        
    *   ![Image 46](https://dhygzobemt712.cloudfront.net/Icons/Dark/24px/CircleCheckYes.svg)
        
        ### Translate your way
        
        Leverage native machine-powered translation or connect with your TMS.
        
    *   ![Image 47](https://dhygzobemt712.cloudfront.net/Icons/Dark/24px/CircleCheckYes.svg)
        
        ### Drive global traffic
        
        Maximize organic traffic to your localized sites with best-in-class SEO.

Frequently asked questions
--------------------------

We're here to help with any questions you have about plans, pricing, and supported features.

### Workspace & Site plans

*   [### What’s the difference between a Workspace & a Site plan?](https://webflow.com/pricing#)
*   [### How many Workspaces can I have?](https://webflow.com/pricing#)
*   [### How many paid Site plans can I have in my Workspace?](https://webflow.com/pricing#)
*   [### Can I cancel my Site and/or Workspace at any time?](https://webflow.com/pricing#)
*   [### What Business plan add-ons are available?](https://webflow.com/pricing#)

### Capabilities & support

*   [### What kind of support does Webflow provide?](https://webflow.com/pricing#)
    
    We provide [customer support via email](https://university.webflow.com/support), and aim to reply to all requests within 48 hours. Those with paid Workspaces get priority support. You’ll also find helpful content on [Webflow University](https://university.webflow.com/) and a host of helpful Webflow customers in our Forum.
    
*   [### Can I host my website somewhere else?](https://webflow.com/pricing#)
    
    You can export your site and host it anywhere you like with any of our paid Workspace plans, no attribution required.**‍**
    
    **Note:** Dynamic content must be exported on a collection-by-collection basis and forms will stop working.
    
*   [### Can my clients or coworkers upload their own content?](https://webflow.com/pricing#)
    
    On the CMS and Business Site plans, clients and collaborators can use the Editor to edit and publish new content anytime.
    
*   [### How much traffic can Webflow hosting handle?](https://webflow.com/pricing#)
    
    [Webflow hosting](https://webflow.com/hosting) scales automatically to handle millions of simultaneous visits and uses Amazon's Cloudfront CDN and Fastly to load websites in milliseconds.
    
*   [### Are Webflow websites SEO-friendly?](https://webflow.com/pricing#)
    
    Yes, Webflow sites are SEO-friendly. Our blazing-fast hosting, standards-based code, free SSL, and mobile-friendliness all help Webflow sites rank in search.
    
*   [### Can I import my website or my code?](https://webflow.com/pricing#)
    
    No, you can only develop websites in Webflow. If you export your code, it can’t be reimported.
    
*   [### Can I cancel my Workspace plan at any time?](https://webflow.com/pricing#)
    
    You can cancel your Workspace plan whenever you’d like. You’ll be downgraded to the free Workspace, which allows 2 free Starter sites. You won’t be locked out of any sites that have paid Site plans.
    
*   [### Does Webflow have an API?](https://webflow.com/pricing#)
    
    Webflow’s REST API allows you to add, update, and remove items from your CMS. Read the [documentation](https://developers.webflow.com/).
    
*   [### How much does a Webflow Certification exam cost?](https://webflow.com/pricing#)
    
    The Webflow Practitioner Certification exam is $100 USD. In some countries and regions, additional taxes (such as VAT) may apply.
